706302f-a.title: Brooklyn: Plymouth Street - Pearl Street
706302f-a.text:
Flyrouth Street, west from Pearl Street, showing at the
right one of the Arbuckle Bros. Coffee Co. building, In order
is also shown the Manhattan and Brooklyn Bridges.
April 4, 1938.
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
